{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回 侥幸脱魔手\n\n朱七七被绯衣少年囚禁，绯衣少年施展易容术与文武双全，企图博取朱七七欢心。朱七七心中只有沈浪，对绯衣少年冷嘲热讽。绯衣少年愤恨之下欲杀沈浪，朱七七激将法使其放她离去。绯衣少年解开朱七七穴道，并助其恢复行动。朱七七逃出密室，经由棺材店“王森记”出口，遇见巨人相助。她来到洛阳城，寻找沈浪，途中遇到流氓赵老大，得知洛阳城中有“铁面温侯”吕凤先和“中原孟尝”欧阳喜。朱七七前往欧阳喜宅院，欲寻求帮助。在欧阳喜宅中，她目睹江湖巨商冷二太爷与奸商贾剥皮的交易，贾剥皮以假翡翠蟾蜍骗人，后又拍卖白衣少女白飞飞。朱七七出于义愤，出价两万两买下白飞飞，却无银两支付。冷二太爷（实为冷二先生）慷慨解囊，揭穿贾剥皮骗局。随后冷二先生出售八百匹骏马，引发石氏三雄与西门蛟、龙常病的争斗。龙常病暗算石氏三雄，王公子（实为绯衣少年王怜花）以暗器反杀龙常病。朱七七得知王怜花即绯衣少年，惊恐逃离。她逃至荒庙，遇青衣妇人，却遭流氓“花花太岁”骚扰。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……无论你变成什么模样，却再也休想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你这些武功是哪里学来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "口中却朗声吟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自传芳酒翻红袖，似有微词动绛本……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绛本",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "垂手乱翻雕玉绊，背人多整绿云鬟……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纤腰怕束金蝉断，寒鬓斜簪玉燕光……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一着青鸟西飞意未回。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "含笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "浑相识",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "意未回",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "帘前春色",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "楼上花榻",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也未必。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非姑娘还识得个才貌与小生相若之人不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘莫非是故意来气我的？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话不用我回答，你也该知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是沈浪死了，又当如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪……沈浪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只怕沈浪不敢前来见我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此地纵有刀山油锅，他也是要来的，只怕你……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可走得动么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我走不动也会爬出去，用不着你伸手来扶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住……住手……放开我……我……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的要我放开你么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我不知道，求求你……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "绯衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是你自己找来的，莫要怪我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "另一人便",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想必是夫人新收容的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来此人竟是个聋子哑巴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人好大的气力，除了他外，世上只怕再也无人能托起这石板了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "当下施礼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢相助……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要我记准这家棺材店，就可带沈浪来了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "她垂首冲到街",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王森记",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "惟恐生意太好；但愿主顾莫来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "她嘴里",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不可能",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "俺的好妹子，你这可是找对人了，洛阳城里那有名的英雄，可不就是俺花花太岁赵老大么……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "劈劈啪啪",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快说，究竟谁是洛阳城最有名的英雄？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "西城里的",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吕凤先，东城里的",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "顾名思义，自是那欧阳喜眼皮较杂，交游较广……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "当下轻叱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳喜住在何处？乖乖的将你家姑奶奶带去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中原孟尝",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧这人气派，倒也不愧",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四字……看来我不妨将这秘密向他白露一二，要他一面探访沈浪下落，一面连络中原豪杰……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "突听一声轻叱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没关系，反正挨揍的是他们，又不是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "强笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘的脾气，倒直爽得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的脾气，你说好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧你模样，想必就是那中原孟尝欧阳喜了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "锦衣汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错……不知姑娘有何见教？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既有",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘这样的客人，在下平日请还请不到，只是今日……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日怎样？莫非你今日没有银子，请不起么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不瞒姑娘说，今日有位江湖巨商冷二太爷已借了这地方做生意，四方贵客，来的不少，是以在下不敢请姑娘……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来此人定是个从未出过家门的公子哥儿，竟比大姑娘还要怕羞……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老爷",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "相公",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人好大的口气，瞧他这副打扮，这副神气，莫非就是江湖传言",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五大恶棍中，那",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_rong_gui",
      "speaker_name": "施荣贵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……好，小弟出三千两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_rong_gui",
      "speaker_name": "施荣贵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……兄弟就出六千两……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_rong_gui",
      "speaker_name": "施荣贵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这翡翠不是整块的……这一双明珠，只是一粒……剖成两半的，大相公，这……这……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇迹",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾大相公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还等什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "不等他",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，俺出一千两……一千五百两……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一千八百两……两千两……三千两……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "突然大喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我出八千两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一万两。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王公子，怎样？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "银子我未带着，但……但过两天……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾大相公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘是你老人家素不相识的，怎能……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾大相公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾大相公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫……莫非她是朱家的千金？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中原孟尝",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人哄然应声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_hai_er",
      "speaker_name": "苦孩儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桐花油五百篓……徽墨一千锭……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_hai_er",
      "speaker_name": "苦孩儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "碧梗香稻五百石。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾大相公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "碧梗香稻米",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_hai_er",
      "speaker_name": "苦孩儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多少？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾大相公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "碧梗稻米",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年公子竟突然笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟出一万五千两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾大相公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一万六千。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台如不愿买了，也无人强迫于你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贾兄说话最好小心些。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_hai_er",
      "speaker_name": "苦孩儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无人出价，这货该是王公子的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也罢，今日就让你这一遭。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你笑什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你怎知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "贾剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但王……王公子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_hai_er",
      "speaker_name": "苦孩儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王公子也是受了我家冷二大爷托咐，要你上当的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_er_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "冷二先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要怎的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "八百匹骏马",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "第二人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟石文豹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "第三人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟石文彪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 795,
      "line_end": 795
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_hu",
      "speaker_name": "石文虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鹰鼻汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那八百匹骏马，是我兄弟要买的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_hu",
      "speaker_name": "石文虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你凭什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_hu",
      "speaker_name": "石文虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你出多少银子？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鹰鼻汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论你出多少，我总比你多一两就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_hu",
      "speaker_name": "石文虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "西门蛟，你莫道我不认得你！我兄弟瞧在道上同源份上，一直让你三分，但你……你着实欺人太甚……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "西门蛟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又待怎样？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_biao",
      "speaker_name": "石文彪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，就让给他吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咔嚓嚓",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_hu",
      "speaker_name": "石文虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是你死，就是我亡，咱们拼了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 854
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_chang_bing",
      "speaker_name": "龙常病",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们在此动手，一来伤了江湖和气，再来也未免太不给欧阳兄面子，依在下看来，不如……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_hu",
      "speaker_name": "石文虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，八百匹骏马咱们是要定了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_wen_bao",
      "speaker_name": "石文豹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙老大这话也有道理……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 874,
      "line_end": 874
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_chang_bing",
      "speaker_name": "龙常病",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，你我击掌为信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 876,
      "line_end": 876
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_chang_bing",
      "speaker_name": "龙常病",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_chang_bing",
      "speaker_name": "龙常病",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "西门蛟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是自然。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 903,
      "line_end": 903
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_hai_er",
      "speaker_name": "苦孩儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是多少？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 907,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "西门蛟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄金两千两整，想来已足够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 909
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "西门蛟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位相公想必是说笑话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 917,
      "line_end": 917
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这三具尸身面前，也有人会说笑么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 919,
      "line_end": 919
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个你也得带回去。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 943,
      "line_end": 943
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 945,
      "line_end": 945
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他袖中已又有一",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也得",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 945,
      "line_end": 945
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这文质彬彬的少年竞有如此惊人的武功，如此狠毒的心肠，当真令人作梦也想不到……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 957,
      "line_end": 957
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪在哪里？他在做什么？他是否也在想我？……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 971,
      "line_end": 971
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宵夜酒菜已备好，朱姑娘可愿赏光？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 973,
      "line_end": 973
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位王公子，乃是洛阳世家公子，朱姑娘只要瞧见招牌上有",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 991,
      "line_end": 991
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三个字，便都是王公子的买卖，他不但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 991,
      "line_end": 991
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王森记",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 993,
      "line_end": 993
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下姓王，草字怜花……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 997,
      "line_end": 997
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……棺材铺……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 999,
      "line_end": 999
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "王公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱姑娘说的是什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1001,
      "line_end": 1001
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1009,
      "line_end": 1009
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱姑娘你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1009,
      "line_end": 1009
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1011,
      "line_end": 1011
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1013,
      "line_end": 1013
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "个人在身后呼喝着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱姑娘……留步……朱姑娘……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1017,
      "line_end": 1017
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱姑娘，带我一起走……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1019,
      "line_end": 1019
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "婆婆，借个火烤好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1041,
      "line_end": 1041
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好我也是女人，否则……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 1067,
      "line_end": 1067
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
